# HelloAPI

HelloAPI is a simple API that allows consumers to view, borrow and return books.

## endpoints [/endpoints]

### Registration [POST]

+ Request (form-data)

        {
        "username": "john doe",
        "email": "johndoeemail@gmail.com",
        "password": "very-very-secret"
        }
        
+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
        "message": "you have successfully registered"
        }
        
### Login [POST]

+ Request (form-data)

        {
        "email": "johndoeemail@gmail.com",
        "password": "very-very-secret"
        }
        
+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
        "message": "you have successfully logged in"
        }

