### Create a New Book [POST]

The admin uses this endpoint to add new books to the library.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "title": "the lost sheep",
            "author": "Jason Pontius",
            "category": "children book",
            "url": "https:///unsplash/pontius"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers


                'content-type': 'application/json',
                'Authorization': 'Bearer {}'.format(access_token)

    + Body

            {
            "title": "the lost sheep",
            "author": "Jason Pontius",
            "category": "children book",
            "url": "https:///unsplash/pontius"
            }
            
### Edit a Book [PUT]

The admin uses this endpoint to edit a book in the library.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "title": "the lost sheep and the silly goat",
            "author": "Jason Pontius pilate",
            "category": "children book",
            "url": "https:///unsplash/pontius"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers
    
        
            'content-type': 'application/json',
            'Authorization': 'Bearer {}'.format(access_token)


    + Body

            {
            "title": "the lost sheep and the silly goat",
            "author": "Jason Pontius pilate",
            "category": "children book",
            "url": "https:///unsplash/pontius"
            }
            
### Delete a Book [DELETE]

The admin uses this endpoint to remove a book from the library.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "title": "the lost sheep and the silly goat",
            "author": "Jason Pontius pilate",
            "category": "children book",
            "url": "https:///unsplash/pontius"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers
    
        
            'content-type': 'application/json',
            'Authorization': 'Bearer {}'.format(access_token)


    + Body

            {
             "message": "book successfully deleted"
            }